            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Clockwork guardians are dedicated to the art of defense. They work best when they operate in small groups, under orders to defend specific locations from intruders. Their standard operating procedure is to force foes out of their respective holdings by use of overwhelming force. <br/><br/>A clockwork guardian is 7 feet tall and weighs 750 pounds."
